Notification of Privacy Statement Changes
Moon Invoice may modify or update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect the changes in our business and practices or applicable laws. Therefore, you should review this page periodically.
90 Days Refund
We are delighted when we see the smile on our customers. We thank you for being our valued customer. Even if you are not associated with us, we strive to make your experience with Moon Invoice a pleasant one with our services and try to go an extra mile; hence, starting now, we are implementing a "Refund Policy."
We offer a 100% money-back guarantee if you are not satisfied with your purchase within the first 90 days.
If you feel that Moon Invoice isn"t the right invoicing platform for your business after trying it out, inform us within 90 days from the date of payment and we will issue you a full refund. Kindly note that refunds won"t be available after 90 days and partial refunds are not issued
Here is how to claim a refund. To place a refund request for your Moon Invoice app purchase:
1. For Apple
Apple currently handles all purchases and refunds in the iTunes App Store. In order to request and receive a refund, you'll need to contact Apple directly. The user can do this through their purchase receipt or application store. Listed below are the step by step guide:
Visit
https://getsupport.apple.com/
Go to iTunes > iTunes Store
Click on "Purchases Billing and Redemption"
Click on iTunes Store account billing
Choose how you would like to contact Apple (by email, chat or talk to apple support now, schedule a call)
2. For Windows
Just like Apple, even Windows processes all the refund requests via Microsoft Account. Listed below are the step by step guide:
Sign in to your Microsoft Account.
From the top menu bar, select Payment & billing > Order history.
Navigate to your Moon Invoice app purchase and select "Request a refund".
3. For Android
Google Play Purchases and PayPal In order for us to process your refund for Google Play Store or PayPal, we request you to primarily contact them first and place your refund request. Furthermore, we will require the following information to process your refund request:
Moon Invoice account ID and email address
Reason for leaving Moon Invoice
Date of Purchase
Once you have submitted your refund request, please allow 10 business days for the refund to process. The refund will be returned in the same method of payment used for the purchase.
4. For Web App (PayPal)
For the PayPal refund procedure, the user needs to follow the below PayPal Refund procedure:
Login into your PayPal Account
Tap on Activity on the top of the page.
Select All Transactions
Tap on the Payment that you wish to refund.
Click on 'Issue my refund.'
You will be asked to enter the refund amount in total or partial. Please enter the amount.
Select Issue refund.
5. For Web App (Paddle)
For the Paddle refund procedure, please connect with Moon Invoice Support Team at
support@mooninvoice.com.
6. For Web App (Stripe)
For the Stripe refund procedure, please connect with Moon Invoice Support Team at
support@mooninvoice.com.
7. User Data Retention Policy - How Long Can Users Retain an Account Post Deletion?
After the deletion of the account, the user will have a 360 days window to restore the account. After 360 days, the account will be permanently deleted from our backup.
